rniture in the office and changing it will drastically affect your health as well as your productivity.";i:18;s:91:"Among the most famous offers at the moment are ergonomic stools chairs and kneeling chairs.";i:19;s:22:"Take a Seat Chairs VS.";i:20;s:23:"Stools in the Art Room.";i:21;s:153:"As if art supplies werent distraction enough for our students the clanking screeching and tipping of furniture in the art room can drive a teacher batty.";i:22;s:49:"Some teachers prefer chairs for art room seating.";i:23;s:54:"Many of us think the grass is greener and WISH we had.";i:24;s:51:"Question about stools from herman miller vs chairs.";i:25;s:139:"Hello I found a local craigslist offer for a mira stool and Im wondering if there is any reason not to get it and go for the chair instead.";i:26;s:18:"Here is a picture.";i:27;s:68:"I dont see a significant difference between the chair and the stool.";i:28;s:59:"A bar stool is a chair you use to sit comfortably at a bar.";i:29;s:64:"The standard height of a bar top is 40-42 inches from the floor.";i:30;s:90:"This means that a good bar stools seat should be somewhere at 29 31 inches from the floor.";i:31;s:102:"The difference of 11 inches is for your legs to rest comfortably without being squashed under the bar.";i:32;s:67:"Standing desk stools are quickly gaining popularity among standers.";i:33;s:58:"Here are the main reasons people use standing desk stools.";i:34;s:126:"More options - simply having another position to choose from is one of the main benefits of getting a standing stool or chair.";i:35;s:111:"Changing positions frequently is one of the keys to staying active at your desk and avoiding pain and soreness.";i:36;s:68:"Some people might think of a chair that wobbles as a faulty product.";i:37;s:74:"However Flexispot wobble stools offer a unique kind of sitting experience.";i:38;s:199:"This is because at Flexispot the wobble stools such as the Height Adjustable Wobble Stool BH2 could be tilted at 15 degrees and swi